ji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T17:54:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一個月前, 港澳辦主任會見匯豐幾位高層，包括行政總裁王冬勝<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1790000\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1790000</a>"},{"pid":"ef31a94eda843618d5db3573bcc6b3ac0a701bea","tid":1790041,"uid":332021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T17:54:41.000Z","msg":"唔洗咁冷靜。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">依家就係要連坐法？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n邊個幫黑警，邊個無抵抗極權反而打擊示威，就係有後果。<br />\n伊朗洗黑錢HSMC都頂到，繼續營運，果七千萬會守唔到。<br />\n<br />\n人喺困境嘅時候，就可以負上較少嘅道德責任。咁又冇得選擇嘅情況下，係咪就冇道德？"},{"pid":"b9c2300e9845831b63dca8193377d74a4d430882","tid":1790041,"uid":95138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T17:55:29.000Z","msg":"滙豐取消佢戶口 搞到4條友要用自己戶口處理<br />\n所以依家俾人告洗黑錢<br />\n<br />\n滙豐絕對唔係無辜<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1578f824dc682454852b33442bcd9a5e14d3323","tid":1790041,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T17:56:48.000Z","msg":"btw冷你老母靜"},{"pid":"c35cd42ef55840257b02af020c0b95076a203d25","tid":1790041,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T17:56:58.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"f9ced02805476253f195d9b987bd5a3b379a3802","tid":1790041,"uid":256320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T17:57:51.000Z","msg":"拉 運動已輸"},{"pid":"84d41dd44d4e08dcab236be67e3811a63a95962c","tid":1790041,"uid":246781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39429e4fa653555d73d5d031b17553e01871e33c","tid":1790041,"uid":95520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c28ac5509db6be255b40fc682db7794e7940201e","tid":1790041,"uid":246781,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8f73342d7cfd1b9d5819c7c81ae5892527154837","tid":1790041,"uid":95520,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T17:46:26.000Z","m